description: Conditional Latent Tree Model for Multi-Object Classification
README.md:
# CLTM
simple python script to extract semantictree structure from fc7 features and labels using kernel conditional embedding framework

Extracted Tree Structure  : http://newport.eecs.uci.edu/anandkumar/Lab/Lab_sub/ObjectClassification.html  for MS-COCO

For more details visit :  http://krishna1188.github.io/cltm

arxiv submission : http://arxiv.org/pdf/1505.00308v1.pdf
